==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Gribble
<hw>Grib"ble</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Cf. Prov. E. grib to
bite.]</ety> <fld>(Zool.)</fld> <def>A small marine isopod crustacean
(<spn>Limnoria lignorum</spn> or <spn>Limnoria terebrans</spn>), which
burrows into and rapidly destroys submerged timber, such as the piles of
wharves, both in Europe and America.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Grice</ent>⟦br⟧
